    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2021-02-23</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2021-03-25T15:38:55Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Electric Credit Access Ready at Sale Act of 2021 or the Electric CARS Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill modifies and extends tax credits for electric cars and alternative motor vehicles. </p> <p>The bill extends the tax credit for new qualified plug-in electric drive motor vehicles through 2031. In addition, the bill modifies the credit to</p> <ul> <li> remove the limitation on the number of vehicles per manufacturer that are eligible for the credit, </li> <li> allow a taxpayer to assign the credit to a financing entity, and </li> <li> allow an unused credit to be carried forward for five years.</li> </ul> <p>The bill also extends through 2031 the tax credits for (1) alternative fuel vehicle refueling property, and (2) alternative motor vehicles. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
